{"tid":1550903,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警察對香港經濟有咩貢獻 竟然大言不慚話人曱甴?","createTime":"2019-09-07T18:32:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T19:59:16.000Z","uid":76745,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"64c4e3bb1d24d439ae3b9341f7b8cd061ad3c848","tid":1550903,"uid":76745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:32:18.000Z","msg":"1. 香港治安好，係因為市民整體擁有良好公民意識，以及高標準嘅道德規範，與警察無關<br />\n2. 香港嘅警民比例之高位列全球頭三，喺一個安全同文明嘅國際城市完全係無必要<br />\n3. 每年200億預算開支，諷刺嘅係買裝備番嚟對付番香港市民<br />\n4. 假設裁減4分1人手，即7000人，以每人平均年薪500,000去計，每年慳番三十幾億，加落醫療開支度，全民受惠<br />\n5. 呢幾個月神憎鬼厭，啲舖頭見到佢地出動就閂閘唔做生意，損失幾多生意額? 佢地啲行為喺國際社會備受讉責，嚴重損害香港國際形象"},{"pid":"f2f71a452858328686baf798c00ce554d424d244","tid":1550903,"uid":160247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:32:50.000Z","msg":"冇貢獻<br />\n<br />\n《願榮光歸香港》 Glory be to thee, Hong Kong<br />\n何以 這土地 淚再流 In angst, tears are shed o&rsquo;er this Land<br />\n何以 令眾人 亦憤恨 With rage, fears are crushed, in arms we stand<br />\n昂首 拒默沉 吶喊聲 響透 We rise, undefiled, our voice shall never die<br />\n盼自由 歸於 這裡 As we yearn, our freedom nighs<br />\n何以 這恐懼 抹不走 With eyes blinded, long it comes the night<br />\n何以 為信念 從沒退後 In faith, banners high, we pledge to fight<br />\n何解 血在流 但邁進聲 響透 Our flesh, sacrificed, our blood shall write this song<br />\n建自由 光輝 香港 Free this Land, &ldquo;Stand with Hong Kong!&rdquo;<br />\n在 晚星 墜落 徬徨 午夜 Stars will fall, and darkness fills the air<br />\n迷霧裡 最遠處 吹 來 號 角 聲 Storms will break, bedazzled by our gallant flares!<br />\n捍自由 We shall strike<br />\n來齊集這裡 This perilous night<br />\n來全力抗對 Determined to fight<br />\n勇氣 智慧 也 永不滅&quot; With hope, with song, with dignity!<br />\n黎明來到 要光復 這香港 Glory enshrined, break our chains! Hold our lines!<br />\n同行兒女 為正義 時代革命 Freedom shall rise! Revolution of our Time!<br />\n祈求 民主 與自由 萬世都 不朽 Liberty thrives, rights divine, in our unending strides<br />\n我願 榮光 歸香港 Glory be to thee, Hong Kong!"},{"pid":"afeaa4ab4559827fa3b7e1a992c3f65a90541b3b","tid":1550903,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:32:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fbeb51c9575586bdb882c0c81a0c93250598dec0","tid":1550903,"uid":123765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:34:15.000Z","msg":"仲要用納稅人錢 全家宿舍 送仔女外國讀書<br />\n香港人仔女就比佢地打死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6a110512214175b5fc3ba0d6870bea4a88ef87c","tid":1550903,"uid":90162,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:36:22.000Z","msg":"冇<br />\n仲敢問返香港人交幾錢稅，仲話自己有份交稅<br />\non9 你有得交稅係因為我老豆老母交稅俾你交稅啊dllm"},{"pid":"64d63fae34eee7e32aaf4bd7e66ef0afd1c3d1a6","tid":1550903,"uid":258566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:37:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"48affc3175727ef1b205783716c556bff7fe859d","tid":1550903,"uid":76745,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fbeb51c9575586bdb882c0c81a0c93250598dec0","tid":1550903,"uid":123765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:34:15.000Z","msg":"仲要用納稅人錢 全家宿舍 送仔女外國讀書<br />\n香港人仔女就比佢地打死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hk